                         Pecan Smoked Tenderloins

Recipe By     : 
Serving Size  : 1    Preparation Time :0:00
Categories    : Bbq List                         Pork

  Amount  Measure       Ingredient -- Preparation Method
--------  ------------  --------------------------------
   1      pound         pork tenderloin
     1/2  cup           soy sauce
