Recipe By     : Tom "Go To Hell Duke" Solomon
Serving Size  : 1    Preparation Time :0:00
Categories    : Bbq List                         Drinks

  Amount  Measure       Ingredient -- Preparation Method
--------  ------------  --------------------------------
   2      tablespoons   nuoc nam
   1      clove         garlic -- minced
     1/4  teaspoon      red chile flakes
   1      shot          vodka
   3      sprigs        creasy greens -- slivered
   1      stalk         celery
   2      tablespoons   Worcestershire sauce
                        V-8 vegetable juice, or tomato juice
   1                    quartered lime

I call this "Tournament Greens Bloody Mary" because the creasy greens start to grow big enough to harvest right around the time of the ACC and NCAA basketball tournaments.

