                Rubs And Spices

  Amount  Measure       Ingredient -- Preparation Method
--------  ------------  --------------------------------
   2      Tablespoons   annatto seeds
     1/2  cup           water
   1      teaspoon      freshly ground allspice
   2      teaspoons     freshly ground black pepper
     1/2  cup           ancho chile powder
   4      teaspoons     kosher salt
